            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center max-w-4xl">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight">Revolutionizing Heart Care in Indonesia with AI</h1>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600">Introducing instant, accurate ECG analysis for early heart disease detection, empowering healthcare professionals across the archipelago.</p>
                <a href="#challenge" class="mt-8 inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">Learn More</a>
