        <section id="challenge" class="py-16 md:py-24">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl">
                <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">Challenges in Indonesia</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-2">The Urgent Burden of Cardiovascular Disease & Military Health</h2>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600">Indonesia faces significant challenges in early heart disease diagnosis due to its vast geography, healthcare access disparities, and limitations in specialized personnel. These issues are acutely amplified within the military setting, impacting personnel readiness and combat effectiveness.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
                    <div class="stat-card md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
                        <div class="section-icon text-red-500 mb-2">💔</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">High Mortality & Morbidity</h3>
                        <ul class="mt-2 text-slate-600 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>Cardiovascular diseases are a **leading cause of death**, accounting for ~**650,000 deaths per year** (2023).</li>
                            <li>Stroke and Ischemic Heart Disease are major contributors to disability (DALY).</li>
                            <li>**Military Relevance:** Heart disease can lead to critical loss of combat assets and reduced operational capacity.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="section-icon text-yellow-500 mb-2">📈</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Prevalent Risk Factors & Officer Health</h3>
                        <ul class="mt-2 text-slate-600 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>**Hypertension:** 30.8% adults (2023), but low treatment adherence.</li>
                            <li>**Diabetes:** 11.7% adults (2023) with rising prevalence.</li>
                            <li>**Obesity:** Affects 1 in 3 adults (2023).</li>
                            <li>**Smoking:** 36.7% adult prevalence (2022).</li>
                            <li>**Military Relevance:** Aging high-ranking officers and a growing tendency for younger onset heart disease among personnel pose significant health risks.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
                        <div class="section-icon text-blue-500 mb-2">🩺</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Critical Cardiologist Shortage</h3>
                        <ul class="mt-2 text-slate-600 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>**Fewer than 1,500 cardiologists** for over 270 million people.</li>
                            <li>Doctor-to-population ratio of **0.4 per 1,000**, well below WHO's 1 per 1,000.</li>
                            <li>**Uneven distribution:** 85% of cardiologists are in West Indonesia (65%+ in Java).</li>
                            <li>**Military Relevance:** Limited access to specialists for military personnel, especially in remote outposts.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="section-icon text-purple-500 mb-2">🏝️</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Geographical Access Gaps & Military Bases</h3>
                        <ul class="mt-2 text-slate-600 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>Many remote islands have **less than one healthcare worker per 10,000 inhabitants**.</li>
                            <li>Healthcare expenditure disproportionately higher in urban areas.</li>
                            <li>Urban dwellers are **1.25x more likely** to use hospital outpatient facilities than rural residents.</li>
                            <li>**Military Relevance:** Remote military bases and difficult terrain severely limit access to comprehensive medical facilities and specialized diagnostics.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                     <div class="stat-card md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
                        <div class="section-icon text-orange-500 mb-2">⏳</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Delayed Diagnosis & Combat Preparedness</h3>
                        <ul class="mt-2 text-slate-600 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>Over **50% of heart attack patients miss the 'golden hour'** for treatment.</li>
                            <li>Disparities in diagnosis and treatment adherence for chronic conditions like hypertension.</li>
                            <li>**Military Relevance:** Delayed diagnosis can compromise individual health and, critically, national security by removing trained personnel from active duty or combat readiness.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

