                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Signals transmitted to central hospital servers for storage.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flow-arrow md:rotate-0 rotate-90">➡️</div>
                    <div class="flow-step bg-blue-100 border-blue-400">
