                </div>

                <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
                    <div class="stat-card md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
                        <div class="section-icon text-green-600 mb-2">💪</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Military Overview: Scale & Distribution</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">The Indonesian National Armed Forces (TNI) are a significant force, critical for national security across a vast and challenging archipelago. Maintaining personnel health is paramount to their operational effectiveness.</p>
                        <ul class="mt-4 text-slate-600 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>Approximately **404,500 active personnel** (2024), ranking among Asia's largest.</li>
                            <li>Units distributed across **15 military regions** on **17,000+ islands**, including remote outposts.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="section-icon text-red-600 mb-2">📍</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Unique Military Healthcare Challenges</h3>
                        <ul class="mt-2 text-slate-600 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>**Personnel Health Risks:** Aging high-ranking officers and younger onset heart disease among personnel.</li>
                            <li>**Geographical Barriers:** Remote military bases, challenging terrain, and dispersed units limit access to specialized medical facilities.</li>
                            <li>**Limited Medical Accessibility:** Shortage of cardiologists in military healthcare, reliance on delayed referrals.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
                        <div class="section-icon text-blue-600 mb-2">🎯</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">AI-ECG: A Force Multiplier</h3>
                        <ul class="mt-2 text-slate-600 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                            <li>**Immediate Risk Assessment:** Rapid 10-second ECG analysis for proactive health management, even in the field.</li>
                            <li>**Preserving Combat Assets:** Prevents unnecessary loss of trained personnel due to undiagnosed cardiac conditions.</li>
                            <li>**Bridging Gaps:** Enables advanced screening in remote military clinics, ships, or airbases without specialists.</li>
                            <li>**Cost-Effective:** Reduces costly medical evacuations for screening/early diagnosis.</li>
                            <li>**Data Security:** On-premise server ensures confidentiality of sensitive military health data.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

